Empath::

"Go make yourself useful somewhere else," Empath orders him.  "I'll 
deal with this ... thing!"  Transforming to her jet mode, she streaks 
into the sky, then dives down at Proto.  Using the Soul Orb's added 
power to shield her thoughts, she sprays plasma fire at her 
shapeshifting adversary.
